  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment completed; all factors assessed and documented. Extensive mesh refinement studies, turbulence model benchmarking, and experimental validation against FDA PIV and hemolysis datasets support the declared Medium assurance level.",
