      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA generic centrifugal pump",
      "description": "Computational velocity fields compared against FDA-published PIV measurements at 2500 RPM and 5 L/min. Mean absolute error in axial velocity < 8% across measurement planes. Turbulence model sensitivity study conducted with k-omega SST and k-epsilon RNG variants; k-omega SST selected based on superior near-wall resolution."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-hemolysis-index-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Relative hemolysis index validation against experimental data",
      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements from three independent laboratories. Model predictions fall within ±15% of mean experimental values across all 5 operating points. Acceptance criterion RH < 1 confirmed for nominal operating conditions."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-mesh-convergence",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh convergence and discretization error quantification",
      "description": "Richardson extrapolation applied across three mesh densities (2.1M, 8.4M, 33.6M cells). Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for shear stress scalar and velocity magnitude. Fine-grid GCI < 2.1% for all QoIs, confirming adequate spatial resolution for hemolysis prediction."
    }
  ],
