      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and traceable release notes consistent with MRL 2 SQA requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 employed under an ISO 9001-registered QMS. Vendor-supplied verification suite demonstrates passing regression tests. Release notes and patch history archived. SQA level consistent with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
