      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence must be demonstrated with residuals reduced by at least 4 orders of magnitude and monitored QoI convergence confirmed.",
      "rationale": "All simulations run to steady-state convergence with residuals reduced 5 orders of magnitude. NIH and velocity magnitude monitored at outlet probe points; variation < 0.01% over final 500 iterations confirms QoI convergence. Double-precision arithmetic used throughout."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
