      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used in validation must be documented as representative of the device population at MRL 2 Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump test specimens fabricated to published dimensional specifications. Three pump units tested across participating laboratories to assess inter-unit variability. Sample representativeness documented. Gradation 1 requirement satisfied."
    },
