      "rationale": "Pump rotational speed in simulation set to 2500 RPM matching experimental nominal. Flow rate boundary condition set to 5.0 L/min matching experimental mean. Fluid viscosity and density matched to within 1% of experimental measurements. Inlet turbulence intensity estimated from experimental facility characterization. Parameter equivalency table provided in technical report appendix."
